data.description:
Beautiful 2 bedroom 2.5 bath townhome with garage located in Cypress Bay in St. Johns County. Downstairs features a large kitchen with eat in area. Kitchen has SS appliances, 42" cabinets and large bar top. Laundry room is located off the kitchen. Living/dining area is carpeted with a glass slider to patio and view of the lake. Power room is also located downstairs for convenience. Upstairs are two nice sized carpeted bedrooms with private baths and walk-in closets. Close to 95, shopping and downtown! Small dog ok with approval. Property is owner managed. Lawn care by HOA

App fee is $50 per person 18 and older. Credit 600+, income 3 times amount of rent. Proof of income and DL required. Small dog ok with approval and $300 non refundable pet fee. Lease fee $75, no smoking.
